            <Char_Desc_45>BIGACE is a PHP and MySQL based Web CMS</Char_Desc_45>
            <Char_Desc_80>BIGACE, a dynamic Web CMS, is a free and professional grade software package.</Char_Desc_80>
            <Char_Desc_250>BIGACE is a dynamic PHP and MySQL based Web CMS. It is a multi-site, multi-language and multi-user Web CMS, whose keypoints are ease of use, speed, flexibility and a simple Installation.</Char_Desc_250>
